snippet.title: Sunshine Manor - Main Trailer
snippet.description:
Sunshine Manor is a classic 8 Bit Horror RPG that sees you as Ada MacReady, trapped inside the titular mansion she must battle the dark forces that have taken her friends. 

Pre-order the game for Nintendo Switch and all other platforms at https://www.fossilgames.com/preorder/

Wishlist Sunshine Manor on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/745730/Sunshine_Manor/
